  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add lamb cubes to the bowl and toss to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Thread lamb, onion, and bell pepper onto skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "Brush the skewers with olive oil and season with salt and pepper.",
    "Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, or until the lamb is cooked to your desired level of doneness.",
    "Transfer the skewers to a plate and squeeze lemon juice over them.",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving."
